data.description: Gorgeous home in Emerald Mountain that is convenient to golf course, entrance to subdivision & grill!   This home has 3 Bedrooms PLUS a bonus room and 2 1/2 bathrooms!  It has a split floor plan with the master en-suite on one side and guest bedrooms on the other.  In the center of the home is your living area, dining room, and eat-in kitchen.  Kitchen has gas stove, stainless appliances, granite countertops, tile back splash and beautiful cabinets.  Master bath has a beautiful tiled walk in shower, double sinks and garden tub.  A unique feature of this home is how the master walk-in closet connects to the laundry room and the laundry room is also accessible to the half bath - which is convenient to the entryway from the garage.  Also, you have a bonus room upstairs that gives you access to the spacious attic.  Step outside to the covered patio & deck area that backs up to woods.  Home has tank-less water heater, gas heat, double pane windows, double garage, sprinkler system & underground fence for pets.  Call your favorite realtor for your personal showing!
